    "name": "血与魔法书",
    "steam_appid": 3152500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras/1370011d2ae44b72b95555cd1bb91ea1.avif?t=1747073605\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras_big/1370011d2ae44b72b95555cd1bb91ea1.avif?t=1747073605 width=800 height=354 /></span>在这款模拟经营回合制战棋游戏中，玩家将置身于一个充满硝烟与传奇的魔幻中世纪大陆。游戏以其独特的回合制战棋玩法，为玩家呈现出一场策略与智慧的盛宴。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras/06eee0cf339694f458bd98556701ff62.avif?t=1747073605\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras_big/06eee0cf339694f458bd98556701ff62.avif?t=1747073605 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战场上，玩家指挥着一支由勇猛骑士、精锐步兵和敏捷弓手组成的军队。每位角色都拥有独特的技能与属性，从骑士的强力冲锋到弓手的远程狙击，再到步兵的坚实防线，玩家需根据地形、敌人分布等因素，精心策划每一步行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras/d10ea357ceed2beb036dc8693108f860.avif?t=1747073605\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras_big/d10ea357ceed2beb036dc8693108f860.avif?t=1747073605 width=800 height=436 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 回合制的设定给予玩家充足的时间去思考战术，无论是迂回包抄、正面强攻还是坚守防御，都需要精准的决策，骑士们可以策马奔腾，迅速切入战场或撤离危险区域，为战局增添了更多的变数和机动性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras/df6c6a5d68ccc19ce620338cfede9e19.avif?t=1747073605\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras_big/df6c6a5d68ccc19ce620338cfede9e19.avif?t=1747073605 width=800 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 画面上，细腻的场景描绘，从广袤的草原到险峻的山城，从繁华的城镇到神秘的森林。音效方面，兵器碰撞声以及士兵们的呐喊声交织在一起，营造出紧张刺激的战斗氛围。 随着游戏的推进，玩家将面临各种强大的敌人，包括凶悍的强盗团伙、纪律严明的正规军以及神秘的异国势力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras/ec0b0367463d9c2db90f5837f5ed1bff.avif?t=1747073605\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152500/extras_big/ec0b0367463d9c2db90f5837f5ed1bff.avif?t=1747073605 width=800 height=612 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过不断地战斗与策略布局，玩家可以提升自己军队的实力，解锁新的技能和装备，拯救这片被恶魔入侵的大陆，在这片充满机遇与挑战的大陆上建立不朽传奇</p>",
